- on-prem software appliance installed in your own data center

- allows integration of your on-prem IT environment with AWS based storage

- Types
  - file gateway
    - files are stored as objects in S3
    - the files are accessed using a nfs or smb mount point, a filesystem mount backed by s3


  - Volume gateway
    stored volume
      - store all data locally
      - back up in s3
      - uses iscsci protocol

    cached volumes
      - s3 is your primary storage
      - frequently accessed data is cached locally, by your storage gateway using on-prem storage
      

  - Tape gateway
